description: Erection of part two buildings of between 9 and 28 storeys (including mezzanine floors and lower ground floor level) comprising 1,130 sq.m of commercial floor space suitable for class A1 (retail), A2 (professional services), A3 (Restaurant), B1 (office or light industrial) And D1 (non-residential institutes) use at ground floor and mezzanine floor level and 298 one, two and three bedroom residential units on the upper floors, as well as 80 on site parking spaces and cycle and motor cycle places.
